Semiconductors and Semiconductor Equipment

Company Overview of POET Technologies Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
POET Technologies Inc. designs, manufactures, and sells semi-conductor products for consumer, data center, high performance computing, military, and commercial applications in the United States, Canada, and Singapore. It offers photonic sensing and optical light source products. The company was formerly known as Opel Technologies Inc. and changed its name to POET Technologies Inc. in June 2013. POET Technologies Inc. is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.


120 Eglinton Avenue EastSuite 1107Toronto, ON M4P 1E2Canada71 Employees



Phone: 416-368-9411

www.opelinc.com







