POET Technologies Inc. Key Developments

POET Technologies Inc. Reports Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the First Quarter Ended March 31, 2017
May 11 17
POET Technologies Inc. reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2017. Total sales in the first quarter were USD 712,600, compared to USD 423,500 in the preceding quarter. Gross margin increased to 41% during the first quarter of 2017, compared to a negative 10% in the fourth quarter of 2016, as higher sales and NRE revenue allowed for better absorption of factory costs. First quarter net loss was USD 3.5 million or USD 0.01 per share compared to USD 3.0 million or USD 0.01 per share in the same quarter one year ago. The loss included non-cash stock-based compensation of USD 894,813 and depreciation & amortization of USD 540,393, compared to USD 1,259,051 and USD 87,844 respectively in the same quarter one year ago.


